{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1681-01_93","head":{"value":"[Stances de la Comete, parlant à Paris]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", janvier 1681 [tome 1], p. 93-98.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Je ne doute point, Madame, que vous n’ayez veu dans vostre Province la Comete qui paroist icy depuis si longtemps. Elle a fait trembler les Foibles ; &amp; le Peuple, que les choses peu communes ne manquent jamais d’épouvanter, en a tiré de fâcheux présages. C’est là-dessus que M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Philbert d’Antibe en Provence, a fait la Piece qui suit.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"LA COMETE, PARLANT A PARIS.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Estant dessus ton Hémisphere,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je vois tes Enfans assemblez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui comme des Cerveaux troublez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un rien font une grande affaire.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils cherchent les lieux écartez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils montent sur des éminences,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les ayant tous écoutez,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je conclus de leurs conférences,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on doit nommer absurditez","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce qu’ils appellent connoissances.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’un ayant regardé longtemps","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si ma couleur est blanche ou bleuë,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Fait de plaisans raisonnemens","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sur ma teste &amp; sur ma queuë.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il dit, tournant son doigt vers moy ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},"Voyez la dangereuse Beste,","Comme sur nous elle s’arreste !","Selon son aspect je prévoy,","Que par quelque horrible tempeste","Elle va tout remplir d’effroy."]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy ? mon aspect est si terrible,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il porte en tous lieux la frayeur !","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et je ne puis estre visible,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que d’abord je ne fasse peur !","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ah, c’est me faire trop d’outrage.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon corps est clair &amp; lumineux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et, si l’on veut ouvrir les yeux,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’on verra bien que mon visage","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne porte rien de furieux","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui prédise le moindre orage.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’autre assure, sans balancer,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que si je parois à la terre,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est pour luy venir annoncer","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les fureurs d’une rude guerre ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais lors que la France en couroux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A dompté l’orgueil teméraire","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une Nation étrangere,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelle Comete d’entre nous","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A prédit les funestes coups","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’on essuyroit de sa colere ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il est mesme de faux Sçavans,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui par ma course vagabonde,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Veulent que j’annonce aux Vivans","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La mort de quelque Grand du Monde.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils disent pour tout argument,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’un Grand nourry dans l’opulence,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est d’un foible tempérament,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui ne peut faire résistance","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A la violente influence","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je pousse du Firmament.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je ne veux d’aucun le trépas ;","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et si, selon eux, on doit plaindre","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les tempéramens délicats,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Loüis le Grand","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"n’a rien à craindre.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce Héros a porté ses pas","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jusques aux plus lointains Climats,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vaincus par son Bras redoutable ;","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et dans ses travaux indomptable,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les chaleurs comme les frimas","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’ont veu toûjours infatigable.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’ils ne cherchent point de détours ;","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy qu’il arrive sur la terre,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tempeste, mort, sanglante guerre,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On n’en peut accuser mon cours ;","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais leur ignorance parfaite,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et leur esprit ambitieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Veut dans une pauvre Comete,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ou dans la matiere des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Trouver l’Autheur pernicieux","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’une faute qu’ils auront faite.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}